I very consciously decided not to namedrop the Order or any characters or groups from the tale series.

This article actually serves no primary worldbuilding purpose. It is, like SCP-2558, intended primarily as an illustration of the kind of Safe-class object I see the Foundation as having all around the world: Inexplicable anomalies which require creative, low-budget solutions to contain.







